		<body>
			<pb n="1"/>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Portland</placeName> <date>July 20<hi rend="sup">th</hi> 1855</date></p>
				<p><addressee>Rev. Isaac Leeser</addressee>&#44; dear sir<lb/> After waiting a long time for your<lb/> valuable <sic>piriodicle</sic>&#44; at last it came<lb/> and am very much pleased with it<lb/> and shall try my best to <sic>sprad</sic> its<lb/> <sic>surculation</sic> in this far <placeName>Western Country</placeName>.<lb/>  I am happy to hear of your safe return<lb/> from your late tour to the <placeName>South&#45;West</placeName>.<lb/>  <persName>Mr Leeser</persName> I must inform you that<lb/> after I got home my Brother moved with<lb/> his <sic>famile</sic> to <placeName>San Francisco</placeName>&#44; and is<lb/> now living there&#44; in passing through the<lb/> state he met <persName>Mrs <hi rend="underline">Whitney</hi></persName>&#61;<hi rend="underline">Alias</hi>&#61;<lb/> <persName>Sarah Ansell</persName>&#44; she complaind very<lb/> much about her Father&#44; She says that<lb/> she send him a Letter in which she Begged<lb/> his Pardon&#44; but he send the Letter back<lb/> unnoticed&#44; <persName>Mr Leeser</persName> all they <add>&#63;</add><lb/> I can write to you is about <sic>som</sic> Rich Gold<lb/> Mines discovered about <sic>for</sic> Hundred miles<lb/> East of this Place which one <sic>sayd</sic> to be<lb/> very Extensive&#44; if all true we will have<lb/> a great harvest&#44; Business has been very good<lb/> since my Return and Expect better times<lb/> yet&#44; in this place are about 25 Jews<lb/> 2 familys&#44; we are trying to <sic>git</sic> a Jewish</p>
			<pb n="2"/>
				<p>Burying ground.  There are <sic>sum</sic> here who want<lb/> to wait a while <sic>yit</sic> so we are all healthy persons<lb/> but I think it is better to prepare before<lb/> hand I have nothing more to write this time</p>
				<p>I remain your <sic>respectfull</sic> Friend</p>
				<p rend="indent(3)"><persName role="author">Moses Abrams</persName></p>
				<p>of the firm of <persName><hi rend="underline">Abrams Brothers</hi></persName></p>
		</body>
